<TIMEX TYPE="DATE">34</TIMEX>, and since <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Wilson</ENAMEX> it has been <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">25</NUMEX>. I do not consider this a deterioration
(this article has an average of <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">17</NUMEX> words per sentence), but it does reflect the
