<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">communication</ENAMEX>. <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">William Henry Harrison</ENAMEX> could talk about the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">governments</ENAMEX> of
<ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Athens</ENAMEX>, <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Rome</ENAMEX>, and the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Helvetic Confederacy</ENAMEX> and expect his <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">audience</ENAMEX> to know what
